| `src/session/` | Claude CLI process management, stream-JSON parser, session pool, worktree isolation |
| `src/state/` | JSON state persistence, file-claim tracking |
| `src/tui/` | ratatui TUI — app state, split-pane UI, activity log |
| `src/github/` | GitHub integration — issues, PRs, labels |
