### Key observations
- The project is **functional and green** — it builds and all tests pass
- There are **20 clippy warnings** (likely dead code from Phase 2 that isn't wired up yet)
- Dependencies are modern (Rust edition 2024, ratatui 0.29, tokio 1, clap 4)
- CI is set up with GitHub Actions (test, clippy, fmt checks)

In short: a healthy early-stage Rust project through Phase 2, with solid test coverage and clean architecture. The main rough edge is the clippy warnings.
